  "firstAcquaintance": "A gambling-loving succubus who wields a musket. She only occasionally remembers she's a succubus and goes to drain life energy.",
  "personality": "Casual and carefree. Gets along well with everyone, but lacks commitment to the team as a whole. Only truly invests herself in things that interest her.",
  "like": "Novelty dice",
  "familiarData": "Berubedo was originally a succubus who joined a wanderer group. Despite having good luck and a love for gambling, she was often called a strange character who forgot her real job (draining life energy).\nIn the group, she frequently clashed with Fenghua and helped Max, who was poor at handling interpersonal relationships. With her life philosophy of one grand gamble per lifetime, she had zero interest in becoming the team leader.\nShe watched Max's team fall apart even though she knew there were problems. After leaving the group, she gambled at an underground city bar but was cheated and lost, getting sold to the slave market as a result.\nShe loves collecting novelty dice of various shapes and materials, but only uses standard dice when actually gambling with others.",
